#  YouTube Video Downloader

A simple web application where users can paste a YouTube video link, select video resolution (360p, 480p, 720p, etc.), and download the video.

## Features
 Paste YouTube Link – Users enter the video URL  
 Resolution Options – Display available resolutions (360p, 480p, 720p, etc.)  
 Download Button – Users can download the selected quality  
 Dark/Light Mode – Simple UI customization  
Mobile-Friendly – Works on phones & tablets  

---

##  Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript (React.js for dynamic UI)  
- **Backend:** Node.js + Express.js  
- **API:** `yt-dlp` (or YouTube Video API)  

---
## Install yt-dlp
pkg update && pkg upgrade
pkg install python
pip install -U yt-dlp

